The curated discovery content in this directory — the experience-card
library, the interest-to-CIP ontology, explanation templates, and
discovery policy definitions — is authored editorial synthesis, distinct
from both the MIT-licensed source code of this repository and the
underlying institutional data (which belongs to the reporting schools
and federal sources).

